item.title: Episode 230: A FEAST FOR CROWS, THE PROPHET: "The King is Dead"
item.description: Hello and welcome to the NotACast, the one true chapter-by-chapter podcast going through A Song of Ice and Fire! In this episode, we kick off the Ironborn storyline in A Feast for Crows with Aeron "Damphair" Greyjoy, the least likeable youth pastor in history, as he tries to get everyone together against the devil...who just happens to be his brother... Feed: https://notacastasoiaf.podbean.com/feed.xml
